            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#AA">
                <p>To Tiberius Claudius Secundinus Lucius Statius Macedonius, son of Tiberius, of the Palatine tribe, first spear of the 4th legion Flavia Felix, 
                    tribune of the first cohort of watchmen, tribune of the 11th urban cohort, tribune of the 9th cohort of the praetorian [guard], first spear again,
                    prefect of the 2nd legion Traiana Fortis, procurator the inheritance tax of Augustus, procurator of the provinces of Lugdunensis and Aquitania
                    for the interests of Augustus, prefect of the grain supply, flamen of the Divine Vespasian. Publius Cassidius Fortunatus, sexvir and Augustalis
                    to his friend. This place was given by decree of the decurions.
                </p>
